tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE renewable_energy_projects (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 project_name VARCHAR(255),
 country VARCHAR(100),
 start_date DATE,
 end_date DATE,
 total_cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
 completed BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE renewable_energy_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    country VARCHAR(100),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    energy_source VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE project_partners (
    partner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    partner_type VARCHAR(100),
    project_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES renewable_energy_projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE renewable_energy_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name TEXT,
    country TEXT,
    project_type TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE funding_sources (
    source_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_name TEXT,
    funding_type TEXT,
    funding_amount DECIMAL,
    project_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES renewable_energy_projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE project_performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    performance_metric TEXT,
    performance_value DECIMAL,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES renewable_energy_projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE renewable_energy_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    country VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    project_cost DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  project_description TEXT,
  location VARCHAR(100),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE countries (
  country_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  country_name VARCHAR(100),
  region VARCHAR(50),
  total_projects INT,
  gdp_per_capita INT
);

CREATE TABLE organizations (
  org_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  org_name VARCHAR(150),
  location VARCHAR(100),
  total_projects INT,
  contact_email VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE technologies (
  tech_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  tech_name VARCHAR(100),
  description TEXT,
  efficiency FLOAT,
  cost_per_kwh FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE project_technologies (
  project_id INT,
  tech_id INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (project_id, tech_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (tech_id) REFERENCES technologies(tech_id)
);

CREATE TABLE project_partners (
  project_id INT,
  org_id INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (project_id, org_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (org_id) REFERENCES organizations(org_id)
);
